data.description: Welcome to 351 St Paul Road! True country living at its best! Tucked away behind an automatic gate, you'll find this 4 bedroom 2 bath home situated on just under 8 acres. The home itself has been meticulously maintained by the current owner with numerous updates done over the years including the addition of a two car carport. Sit back and relax on the screened in porch while taking in all the peace and quiet that this property has to offer!
